\par \b Black to Play.\b0
\par To  begin with, white's group in the corner is perfectly alive.
\par
\par Then,
\par
\par Black plays at 1 and white makes a hanging connection with 2.
\par Something is wrong. White has made a mistake meaning there is a chance for black.
\par }
