Diagram 1 (Black Mistake)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Now it is black's turn to make a mistake by playing dansu at 1. It is like a mistake competition. White connects at 2 and that's it.
\par
\par Some might think this is natural.
\par However, there is a move to capture white.
\par }
