\par When black plays at \'a1\'e3, where should white play?
\par
\par Is it white 1? No, white gets into trouble again.
\par
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj The life-saving moves for white are \b\f1 A\b0\f0 , \b\f1 B\b0\f0 , or \b\f1 C\b0\f0 .
\par \pard
\par Please check for yourself.
\par
\par }
